reviewText: I kinda new what i was getting into, i am a big fan of the sounds that Voice Crack create as someone that probably will never get the chance to see them live it was nice to get a glimpse at them performing it was both interesting and  pleasurable . My only complaint is I would of liked an explanation as to how they were creating such sounds with what seemed like a piano string strung across a room, but i understand it was a performance and of course there not going to stop to say 'hey this is". So all in all i  love this.
